      <title>据消息人士称，中国 Trustar 为持有麦当劳中国股份的公司筹集了 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，信达资本已为延续基金募集 10 亿美元，该基金将持有这家中国私募股权公司在麦当劳中国大陆和香港业务的控股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:52:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
